This code:
```python
from gutenberg.acquire import load_etext
from gutenberg.cleanup import strip_headers

text = strip_headers(load_etext(50333)).strip()
print(text[:10])
text = strip_headers(load_etext(50334)).strip()
print(text[:10])
```

Produces:
```
Traceback (most recent call last):
