    name0 = BarBarBarBarB(
        pool_size=(
            2, 2), strides=(
            2, 2), padding=""food"")(Food)
#          ^-- here must be 4 extra spaces
```

Position of newline symbols looks a bit strange. Furthermore in the second situation amount of spaces is not correct.",{},{}
