3285,IssuesEvent,2017-09-28 15:27:03+00:00,6536534,amueller/word_cloud,449558,amueller,,,closed,Word Frequency and displayed size not correctly proportional,[],[],1,"I'm trying to integrate word_cloud into my app, but the resulting images seem to be consistently misleading.

