4115,IssuesEvent,2015-12-01 20:36:04+00:00,21791607,maxtepkeev/architect,5129564,LordNoteworthy,,,closed,Data is inserted in both child tables and parent table,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/maxtepkeev/architect/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': 'cc317c'}]",[],7,"Hello,

Thank you so much for this awesome tool.

