5789,IssuesEvent,2017-06-25 18:12:14+00:00,28577939,CamDavidsonPilon/lifetimes,884032,CamDavidsonPilon,,,closed,Optimizer for fit method,[],[],1,"I found, that optimizer for `_fit` was changed from `minimize` to `fmin` in utils with [that commit](https://github.com/CamDavidsonPilon/lifetimes/commit/bc06a6c73932e888c034df1c6a596ca28375e728#diff-48a7adefd56b3316f39206b07dadd6f5). I have some questions: 
- why *Nelder-Mead* algorithm was finally chosen?
