6650,IssuesEvent,2016-08-08 17:19:58+00:00,11697046,mfogel/django-simple-email-confirmation,1469823,mdamien,,,closed,New release PyPI installation failure,[],[],2,"@mdamien maybe you're already aware, but just in case...

