7411,IssuesEvent,2018-04-19 17:25:06+00:00,40684033,mozilla/sops,2260567,autrilla,131524,mozilla,opened,"Document SOPS ""recipes""","[{'id': 907500359, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/sops/labels/Priority%20-%20Medium', 'name': 'Priority - Medium', 'color': 'f78fb9', 'default': False}]",[],0,"SOPS can be very useful when combined with additional tools. Creating a list of ""recipes"" that use SOPS would be interesting and inspire creative usages of SOPS. A few examples:

- Use an SSH key encrypted in a SOPS file to log in to a remote server (#280)
- Operate on stdin (#330)
- Use SOPS to encrypt Kubernetes secrets on-disk (https://frederic-hemberger.de/articles/manage-kubernetes-secrets-with-sops/)
- Use SOPS as a secret backend for Ansible (#303)",{},{}
