7421,IssuesEvent,2018-03-20 13:43:15+00:00,525316,mozilla/bleach,820826,willkg,131524,mozilla,opened,clean drops attribute namespaces,[],[],0,"From https://github.com/mozilla/bleach/pull/361#pullrequestreview-105159247

This works fine:

```
allowed_attrs['svg'] = ['xmlns', 'xlink']

<svg xmlns=""http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"" xmlns:xlink=""http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"">alert</svg>
--
<svg xlink=""http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"" xmlns=""http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"">alert</svg>
```

This drops the namespace:

```
allowed_attrs['svg'] = ['xmlns', 'xmlns:xlink']

<svg xmlns=""http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"" xmlns:xlink=""http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"">alert</svg>
--
<svg xmlns=""http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"">alert</svg>
```

This should work correctly in Bleach `clean`.",{},{}
