After I removed the blueprint and the relative endpoint, I run the following commands:
`$ pip install -e .[all]`
`$ celery worker -A invenio_app.celery -l INFO -f celerylog.log -c 1 --purge`

Here you can find the commit with the changes I made:
https://github.com/ChiaraBi/asclepias-broker/commit/0286ee01a70f7d5a4fbc22923e43de1feb304c19

And here you can find the previous version of `views.py`, where everything works as expected:
