10485,IssuesEvent,2016-02-08 13:43:19+00:00,35882519,zalando/connexion,4091505,jvgutierrez,1564818,zalando,opened,Issue with endpoints with body and path params,[],[],0,"I'm having problems creating an endpoint like this one:
```yaml
  /test-mixed-params/{path_param}:
    post:
      summary: Test mixed params (path and body)
      operationId: fakeapi.hello.test_mixed_params
      parameters:
        - name: path_param
          type: string
          in: path
          required: true
        - name: body_param
          in: body
          required: true
```

When a request is sent to this endpoint the following error is generated:
```
TypeError: test_mixed_params() takes exactly 2 arguments (1 given)
```

