11564,IssuesEvent,2017-02-22 01:10:27+00:00,82338450,ripple/dactyl,7515597,mDuo13,3165523,ripple,opened,Make link substitution a filter and move it to a sub-field,"[{'id': 542082325, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/ripple/dactyl/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]",[],0,"Right now the link substitution behavior is kind of confusing and janky. It should be possible to implement it as a filter so it's not turned on by default.

