Navigate to the learners tab and check the groups section, Its is not updated.
![group4](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13453618/27081866-0579c4d2-5060-11e7-8001-a00b9f883b65.png)
Navigate to exam and try to allocate the exam that was created earlier, no groups on drop down:
![group5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13453618/27081881-1fd6a200-5060-11e7-87c0-71d777deb195.png)
Refresh page:
![group6](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13453618/27081889-2cb4fe5e-5060-11e7-93f2-1f011fe532c7.png)
The changes are reflected:
![group7](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13453618/27081905-361a7424-5060-11e7-8d9f-5c133d629b12.png)
