11887,IssuesEvent,2017-08-08 23:49:30+00:00,49976939,learningequality/kolibri,1680573,rtibbles,3926525,learningequality,closed,popup can be intrusive in certain content types,"[{'id': 492816719, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/learningequality/kolibri/labels/TASK:%20ux%20update', 'name': 'TASK: ux update', 'color': 'E2D1E0', 'default': False}]",[],3,"The popup makes sense when we have a definitive signal that the item is ""finished"" - e.g. for exercises

