12493,IssuesEvent,2015-07-27 12:32:21+00:00,14151539,influxdb/influxdb-python,8983016,dschallis,5713248,influxdb,closed,Integers being written as float64,[],[],1,"One thing I noticed - if I create a point using an int value using e.g. curl, it gets created in InfluxDB as an integer. If I send the same point from the influxdb module, it gets created as a float64.

E.g. if I create a point with:

