12508,IssuesEvent,2018-04-08 23:54:14+00:00,14121294,cuthbertLab/music21,8087473,Reichenbachian,5853935,cuthbertLab,opened,Multi-Duration Chord in MXL,[],[],0,"According to a [musicxml issue](https://github.com/w3c/musicxml/issues/106) and the last line of their [documentation on chords](https://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/the-midi-compatible-part/chords/) as of musicxml v3.0, multi-duration chords should be allowed, given that the longest duration comes first. Music21 doesn't have this enabled. It would be greatly appreciated if it could be brought up to compatibility with musicxml v3.0. 

Thanks for all the wonderful work!",{},{}
12527,IssuesEvent,2016-03-17 08:45:44+00:00,40702744,manahl/pytest-plugins,7449642,skolsuper,5859004,manahl,opened,Async tests with rethinkdb,[],[],0,"First, thanks very much for sharing this package, it's awesome!

