jyou/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/djyou/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",10,"Whilst https://github.com/Azure/azure-cli/pull/859 has been merged, it includes `mgmt_acr` in the module code.

