14076,IssuesEvent,2015-10-07 16:32:55+00:00,24777832,galaxyproject/planemo,63959,peterjc,7937847,galaxyproject,opened,Complete action coverage in planemo dependency_script ,[],[],0,"The initial ``planemo dependency_script `` implementation https://github.com/galaxyproject/planemo/commit/f798c7e29b2276ce68b828e72fc6a6460c73792b (see #303 and #310) only covers some of the actions available in a ``tool_dependencies.xml`` file.

