I can see how SYN package arrive after that SYN, ACK (10:30:33.975833000>10:30:33.970595000). Both (my computer and server) are ntp synchronized [ but I think they are not enough syncrhonized because of this issue ]. Maybe I can force my clock to be 300 ms unsynchronized ...

How could I fix this issue ? I cannot test on another jump host ( i was going to test with a phisical server (and not virtual)) but I cannot :(

