14437,IssuesEvent,2017-06-01 09:44:01+00:00,41756998,pytest-dev/pytest-xdist,67612,matthew-brett,8897583,pytest-dev,opened,pip install fails with missing six module - probably bug in setuptools,[],[],0,"Summary - something in setuptools just broke your install.

Either of:

* `pip install git+https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-xdist`
* `pip install pytest-xdist`

fails with (example):

