14529,IssuesEvent,2015-12-10 06:14:23+00:00,1151051,django-oscar/django-oscar,242997,monokrome,9057806,django-oscar,opened,Repository.get_default_shipping_method should has a confusing name.,[],[],0,"It looks like `get_default_shipping_method` is actually supposed to return the shipping method for the current checkout session. This is very confusing, because it is named in a way that implies that it is only expected to give the default shipping method.

I would like rename it to `get_current_shipping_method` with a fallback to the name `get_default_shipping_method` for legacy support. I will create a pull request if this seems reasonable, but would like to get other thoughts on this issue.",{},{}
