14751,IssuesEvent,2016-03-29 02:02:59+00:00,26516210,letsencrypt/letsencrypt,1434096,brianmorton,9289019,letsencrypt,opened,Failing on email address,[],[],0,"First time user, so it could definitely be my fault, but I read the docs briefly and ran
