14837,IssuesEvent,2017-11-03 17:30:39+00:00,26876372,dateutil/dateutil,1377457,pganssle,9849410,dateutil,closed,Parser fails to parse 'DDmonYYYY',"[{'id': 149492525, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/dateutil/dateutil/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}, {'id': 177049992, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/dateutil/dateutil/labels/parser', 'name': 'parser', 'color': 'd4c5f9', 'default': False}]",[],2,"```python
>>> dateutil.parser.parse('13NOV2017', fuzzy=True)
datetime.datetime(2017, 4, 13, 0, 0)  # --- today's date

>>> dateutil.parser.parse('13NOV2017', fuzzy=True, dayfirst=True)
datetime.datetime(2017, 4, 13, 0, 0)  # --- today's date
```
Without fuzzy, it raises an error.

