15540,IssuesEvent,2017-10-12 14:25:27+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,14854996,GuerricChupin,11668813,Z3Prover,opened,Z3 gives different answer depending on the value of `fixedpoint.xform.inline_eager`,[],[],0,"I have the [following code](https://gist.github.com/GuerricChupin/ff17ab16fe1e4a9698c33aee76e2bc74) (if you are interested in why it exists, please read my [StackOverflow question](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/46604222/z3-giving-unexpected-result-with-the-pdr-engine)).

