16186,IssuesEvent,2016-02-25 12:46:47+00:00,31315021,Kinto/kinto,229453,Natim,13413813,Kinto,closed,Filter nested JSON objects fields.,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Kinto/kinto/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Kinto/kinto/labels/scope:%20cliquet', 'name': 'scope: cliquet', 'color': 'd4c5f9'}]",[],1,"Today it is possible to use the ``_fields`` query parameter to choose the list of fields we want.

In case of kinto-attachment, a nested object has been created, in case of our Fennec OTA use case we have this kind of records:

