17618,IssuesEvent,2018-08-28 07:12:28+00:00,50646767,raiden-network/raiden,310139,hackaugusto,19666847,raiden-network,reopened,Rest API unhandled exceptions should crash the node,"[{'id': 318426947, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWwzMTg0MjY5NDc=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/raiden-network/raiden/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]","[{'login': 'andrevmatos', 'id': 587021, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjU4NzAyMQ==', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/587021?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/andrevmatos', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/andrevmatos/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}, {'login': 'jomuel', 'id': 11137424, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjExMTM3NDI0', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/11137424?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/jomuel', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jomuel/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",2,"## Problem Definition

After a lot of debugging, it was made clear that `gevent` already bubbles up unhandled exceptions up to the parent greenlet, which is the expected behavior. Except when the greenlet is spawned by the `APIServer`, where flask handles all exceptions and return `500` errors, where we want the node to crash. We must make sure the node also exits if any unhandled exception happens in the greenlet which handles a request.
Related: #2123 
Requires: #2171 ",{},{}
