### Description
Is it possible to have a plugin for girlfriendsfilmsvod.com (NSFW)? 

### Reasoning
To be perfectly honest, I have a limited understanding of how exactly this works, I'm still learning. Please forgive me if I use the incorrect terminology.

Until recently, RTMP Dump Helper sufficed for my stream capture needs, until I discovered that HD films from this studio are not readily available for download. Other than low-res DVD's, VOD is the only alternative with these folks. Once a scene is purchased from this site you find out that the advertised (perfectly legal and allowed) download is low resolution, and can only be streamed in HD. I've tried a few different ways of saving a copy of that stream, all of which failed. I even tried other VOD sites, to see if I could catch their streams, but they all offered the low-res download, and none had the HD stream. Short of screen capture _(shudders)_ you gentlemen/ladies are my last best hope.

I don't think DRM would have to be violated, but the plugin might have to support username and password authentication, or cookie sniffing. I think the streaming method being used is called Dash. The stream is avc mp4 video, with a bitrate of 4994kbps. Audio is mp4a.

### Explicit stream URLs to test

1. This is the address in the browser (Firefox 54.0b1) - https://www.girlfriendsfilmsvod.com/_player.php?video_id=330360&ps_id=3464715&bitrate_index=5
The value for bitrate index changes depending on whether or not HD streaming quality was selected. Ranges from 1 (low) to 5 (max).

2. I believe this is the... manifest? file, or something important - https://astream.hotmovies.com/stream/330/330360/330360.ism/330360.mpd?ssauth=26816865-330360|0|2681-20170426050258-41d82fd468355b82ef6dbbb6c5c6f2ed&min_bitrate=350

