## Docker Compose file
```
version: '2'
services:
  localstack:
    image: localstack/localstack:latest
    ports:
      - ""4567-4583:4567-4583""
      - ""8080:8080""
    environment:
      - SERVICES=kinesis:4568,dynamodb:4569
      - DEFAULT_REGION=us-east-1
      - DOCKER_HOST=unix:///var/run/docker.sock
    volumes:
      - ""/tmp/localstack:/tmp/localstack""
      - ""/var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock""
